column2: select top #  S.ra as sdss_ra, S.dec as sdss_dec, W.ra as wise_ra, W.dec as wise_dec,  S.psfmag_r as r, S.psfmag_z as z, W.w1mpro as w1, W.w2mpro as w2, W.w3mpro as w3, W.w1mpro-W.w2mpro as &&&, W.w2mpro-W.w3mpro as &&& from wise_xmatch as X  join wise_allsky as W on X.wise_cntr = W.cntr  join photoTag as S on X.sdss_objid = S.objid where S.nchild = #
